results.deck: German developer famous for the "ANNO" series founded in 1993 by Adi Boiko and Wilhelm Hamrozi. Sunflowers was bought by Ubisoft in 2007
results.description: Sunflowers Interactive released a total of three Anno games as well as various expansion packs for each of those games. These games are Anno 1602, Anno 1701 and Anno 1503. Note that the game Anno 1404 has been released by Ubisoft, who aquired Sunflowers Interactive in 2007. Besides the Anno games, Sunflowers is also credited for developing ParaWorld and Knights of Honor.
